headline.print_headline: It's Simple Really Says McIlroy, Just Process and Spot
headline.main: It's Simple Really Says McIlroy, Just Process and Spot

lead_paragraph: For Rory McIlroy the secret of his stunning victory at the Open on Sunday came down to two rather unremarkable words: process and spot.
